                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1142" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MGEC-0019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8721 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">关于厦门华夏恐龙世界建设的社会经济构想</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">-</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">詹圣泽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“华夏恐龙世界”旅游项目</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">社会经济；文化产业；海峡旅游；区域经济；项目研究；社会就业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">social economy; culture industry; Strait Tourism; regional economy; research projects; social employment</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中共十七届五中全会和我国的十二五规划明确提出：推动文化大发展大繁荣，提升国家文化软实力，发展新型文化业态，推动文化产业成为国民经济支柱性产业。这表明，我国已把文化产业提高到国民经济发展战略的前所未有的高度来认识和对待。国务院对厦门的城市定位是国际性港口旅游风景城市。厦门面对旅游资源丰富、景点相对集中、地域腹地偏小、难以久留游客的特点，如何凭借客流量大的基础优势努力挖掘潜在的旅游客源？如何更好地贯彻落实好“推动文化产业成为国民经济支柱性产业”的精神？并以此为契机又好又快地进一步推进厦门旅游文化产业的大力发展？本文就“华夏恐龙世界”这一文化旅游项目的建设进行了调研并提出了一些构想。本调研报告得到了中共厦门市委副书记钟兴国同志（博士）和海投集团领导的充分肯定，钟兴国书同志批示：“这是一篇经过认真思考的分析报告，可供海投领导在研究该项目时参考”。该项目的合作框架协议业已签定，目前已经立项兴建。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The seventeen session of the Fifth Plenary Session of the Twelfth Five-Year Plan of our country and puts forward clearly: promote the development and prosperity of culture, enhancing soft power of national culture, development of new cultural industry, promote the cultural industry has become the pillar industries for the national economy. This shows, our country has regarded the cultural industry to national economic development strategy hitherto unknown height to understand and treat. The State Council to Xiamen city positioning is an international port city tourism landscape. The face of Xiamen rich tourism resources, the relative concentration of hinterland, area attractions, visitors to stay small features, by virtue of traffic advantage efforts to tap the potential of tourism? How to better implement the &quot; promote the cultural industry has become the pillar industries for the national economy &quot; of the spirit? And as an opportunity to further promote sound and fast development of Xiamen tourism culture industry? In this paper, the &quot;China dinosaur world &quot; this cultural tourism project construction undertook research and put forward some conception. This investigation report was Deputy Secretary of the CPC Xiamen committee Comrade Zhong Xingguo ( PhD) and sea Investment Group Leadership full affirmation, bell country book comrades wrote: &quot;this is an after careful thought, analysis, for the sea cast leadership in research of the item reference &quot;. The project cooperation framework agreement has been signed, at present already project approving construction.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">-</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013-03</td>
                            </tr>
